                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Iteration 2: Lo-Fi -->
                        <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-[85%] md:w-[600px] aspect-[4/3] bg-surface rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden group relative pointer-events-none">
                            <img src="img/ui/UI-02.png" alt="Mid Fidelity" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white border border-white/10">Phase 2: Structure</div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Iteration 3: Hi-Fi -->
                        <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-[85%] md:w-[600px] aspect-[4/3] bg-surface rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden group relative pointer-events-none">
                            <img src="img/ui/UI-03.png" alt="High Fidelity" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white border border-white/10">Phase 3: Visuals</div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Pagination Dots -->
                    <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mt-4">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#829DF1]"></div>
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20"></div>
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- ITERATION CARDS (No Vertical Line) -->
                <div class="space-y-12 mb-24 mt-24">
                    
                    <!-- Issue 1 -->
                    <div class="pl-2">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The "Banner Blindness" Issue</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-6 font-light"><strong class="text-slate-300">Problem:</strong> In V1, we used a banner on top of the image to say "Recommended." Users completely ignored it, thinking it was an ad.</p>
                        
                        <div class="bg-[#0f172a]/80 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl">
                            <p class="text-[#829DF1] text-lg font-serif italic">The Fix:</p>
                            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mt-2">We changed it to a high-contrast "Chip" inside the content area and added a subtle glow effect. Visibility improved immediately.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Issue 2 -->
                    <div class="pl-2">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The "Scroll Fatigue" Issue</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-6 font-light"><strong class="text-slate-300">Problem:</strong> On the Property Overview page, we placed recommendations at the very bottom. Heatmaps showed 0% of users reached that far.</p>
                        
                        <div class="bg-[#0f172a]/80 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl">
                            <p class="text-[#829DF1] text-lg font-serif italic">The Fix:</p>
                            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mt-2">We moved the recommendation section <strong>UP</strong>, placing it immediately after the facility listing. This catches the user *before* they abandon the page.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 5. CONCLUSION -->
            <section class="reveal mt-24">
                <div class="border border-white/10 rounded-2xl bg-[#0f172a] p-8 md:p-12 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif italic text-white mb-6">Reflection</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6">
                            Since this was a capstone project, we couldn't measure live post-launch metrics. However, the qualitative feedback from our testing sessions was clear: <strong class="text-white">Users feel safer when the system curates for them.</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-muted text-sm">
                            If implemented, we hypothesize a significant reduction in time-to-book and an increase in return user rate (CLV), as the platform transforms from a directory into a concierge.
                        </p>
                        
                        <!-- Tech Stack -->
                        <div class="mt-12 border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
                            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
